lead_paragraph: Ten-man Italy earned a hard-fought 3-1 win away to Israel in their opening Group G World Cup qualifier on Monday after defender Giorgio Chiellini was sent off early in the second half.

headline.print_headline: Ten-Man Italy Battle to 3-1 Win Over Israel
